title: Argentina : internet user penetration 2017 to 2023
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Share of population, containing a total of 7 data points.
In general Share of population has rose over the Year.
Share of population is slightly increasing from 2017 to 2021, and lastly roughly constant from 2021 to 2023.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2017 and 2018.
Maximum Share of population, about 94.0 was reported at Year 2023
The lowest Share of population, of value 77.0 was reported at Year 2017
